responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "7864F4C7466D91A54C0046AD37E59345", "Heavy Glint! That is what I desire. Enough to build a castle far from this wretched land of laws. I know someday father\'s wealth shall pass on to we sisters. Until then I shall keep my chest ready for glint.")
